{"tid":987804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道：支那提出進口一萬億美元貨品　美帝認為進度太慢","createTime":"2019-01-19T14:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T04:22:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"44f93f7fd257fea18094661c0c6b4ca04db6d158","tid":987804,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438948-20190119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438948-20190119.htm&d=JPpRKBlMaYkJtE66RXWZXF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6f618fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1438948-20190119.htm&h=e6f3b2d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1438948-20190119.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rlglobal.com/Content/images/ss_pg-importexport_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frlglobal.com%2FContent%2Fimages%2Fss_pg-importexport_1.jpg&h=5746737d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那國務院副總理劉鶴本月底會到訪華盛頓，與美國官員舉行新一輪貿易談判。<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社引述消息人士指，支那上星期在北京的副部級會談中，提出未來六年從美國進口超過一萬億美元的商品，將對美貿易順差從去年的3230億美元，到2024年降至零。<br />\n<br />\n不過消息稱，美方認為進度太慢，要求支那於兩年內就要消除雙方貿易不平衡的問題。雙方仍未有定案。"},{"pid":"9742d3e381a3191495e16168bece1ebe403fc3f3","tid":987804,"uid":18955,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"又想拖<br />\n共黨答應得嘅野<br />\n自古以黎都係扼鳩你<br />\n有邊樣會找數埋單<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n五十年不變<br />\n高度自治<br />\n港人治港<br />\nWTO 關稅<br />\n中英聯合聲明<br />\n下刪一千字"},{"pid":"58b629adc875d7880e6f22b75d3b0b6f316e0845","tid":987804,"uid":41545,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"的確係慢 呢90日無咩進展直接收支那皮好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55f831923ca97d2e52024ee830a9bf852279d03","tid":987804,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9742d3